Notice on third-party datasets and models redistributed in this repository:

The IBM Telco Customer Churn v11.1.3 Excel files included under `data/raw/`
are © IBM Corporation. They are redistributed here for educational
reproducibility purposes as part of a take-home challenge for Artefact.
All rights to the dataset remain with IBM. Original source:
https://community.ibm.com/community/user/businessanalytics/blogs/steven-macko/2019/07/11/telco-customer-churn-1113

The synthetic customer verbatims under `data/external/verbatims.parquet`
were generated by the author using Qwen2.5-7B-Instruct (Alibaba, Apache 2.0).
The generated text and the generation methodology are released under the MIT
License above.

The sentence-transformers model `all-MiniLM-L6-v2` (Microsoft Research, Apache
2.0) is loaded at runtime and is NOT redistributed in this repository.
